uld contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=916ec1fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"8b9e09354c8741470a9d77e703c53a6f87218975","tid":1396282,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da9620ff22d62e328e0b38854a829d90c6b5d621","tid":1396282,"uid":59016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"全部人都諗唔到邊個出口出 係入面係咁轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"可以轉走完再轉過 一定合法"},{"pid":"7ef7ce728489bb439463cd9071d7229b1d710ef2","tid":1396282,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:01:55.000Z","msg":"觀塘 九龍城 象鼻山 上水 大圍 <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇?"},{"pid":"ebf49ebe2b6fc28e2b3b11cf13a5f646e9b6d6e9","tid":1396282,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4caa0ab1e2d8a90bd3f4ab981172ce98a4f7024c","tid":1396282,"uid":262022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97606f1e2b094636c4